Global rice paddy greenhouse gas emissions have doubled over the past six decades driven by area expansion and intensified residue incorporation
                    Jingting Zhang 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-5041-36291,2, Hanqin Tian 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-1806-40912,3, Xin-Zhong Liang 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-5047-31351,4, Josep G. Canadell 
